{"tid":1011140,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評 蟹王麵","createTime":"2019-02-06T13:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T21:12:11.000Z","uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f9831ab320a7d291dcc640132a866caf4a1e2e45","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始成日聽到有人吹奏蟹王麵好似好勁咁，又話咩好難買。<br />\n<br />\n我由細到大都係食開出前一丁，乜野蟹王麵真係無咩聽過，更加未食過。<br />\n<br />\n今日咁啱見到超市居然有賣，5包廿幾蚊，個包裝十足80年代年產物咁。<br />\n<br />\n為咗日後可以扮下老屎忽笑下啲未食過蟹王麵嘅人，決定買黎試下。"},{"pid":"2483113ab26f1afaae6eeffb3b6a32df6d51623c","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/06/220022_88f6fa6695b4d2d5f22492f1c7b44ce0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2F220022_88f6fa6695b4d2d5f22492f1c7b44ce0.png&h=7e96f2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包裝真係唔知想點，不過有日本製三個字，應該唔會伏得去邊。"},{"pid":"f693aff4c530c86357cd596ef2fc0782da032287","tid":1011140,"uid":33698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"cbcdb54e3c767db49a16fd6efd6a6aeb1a10bae8","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"煲緊水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/06/220538_ca80645a45e78da264ad509617f1e896.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2F220538_ca80645a45e78da264ad509617f1e896.png&h=3becaf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個麵餅望落同丁麵差唔多"},{"pid":"ba1ebed40ad31bd63a4c2b1ba4c01d8e32caa150","tid":1011140,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"手機一鍵留名"},{"pid":"c9b5313f65abe53d14bd4f5231097d6cf064dfd0","tid":1011140,"uid":23988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"食得未？"},{"pid":"d332c290d84c65726930ef3d80cdf40a931690c4","tid":1011140,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"一般貨色"},{"pid":"9541e9e3bd8b423f842697095316e2154333a090","tid":1011140,"uid":168865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"冇料到"},{"pid":"f7619ccf83d37675ca69f9f325138eb133e60b1c","tid":1011140,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"35a47f8be3509bb4e745ac3537763467d628e8a4","tid":1011140,"uid":102781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係太特別"},{"pid":"cbe4d024b90a736e978fe306f05750e2bf3e09ac","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/06/221529_790099d9e3e3b3b76200ce6027018096.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2F221529_790099d9e3e3b3b76200ce6027018096.png&h=0b5a0b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湯粉望落無一丁咁深色"},{"pid":"8923a5f83d0ce154298a60cdd5bd0976dc4e49f4","tid":1011140,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2137b86d8f17d9c52c9c10dd5b75b0dab2d7735c","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/06/221816_bf1d341775ccadd90dd80b6ef1d480f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F06%2F221816_bf1d341775ccadd90dd80b6ef1d480f4.png&h=9f5ed0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映太陽之蛋<br />\n<br />\n現在試食中"},{"pid":"4cffb7ff51edae56088a2296a205f2efc8b69b56","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁多人未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16f744a0c1ea62a868c40a5a81dc603563f2119","tid":1011140,"uid":27482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:21:24.000Z","msg":"其實好普通"},{"pid":"f5da6582d4e5a14e2bab9861558d8c7408a34cca","tid":1011140,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"10d673b39fd94141b8d5f655c15c3e32ae323b7e","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"食完<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係淡味版嘅麻油味出前一丁，個湯易入口，但唔會好似一丁咁會飲多幾啖。<br />\n<br />\n個麻油無出面一丁咁香。<br />\n<br />\n面質滑過一丁，不過無咁彈，已經有過冷河。個感覺似浸左好耐嘅米線。<br />\n<br />\n同出前一丁比較嘅話，我偏好出前一丁少少，但兩者質素唔係相差咁遠。<br />\n<br />\n其實都係我預計之內，咁嘅質素亦都唔奇怪點解咁少見有得賣。<br />\n<br />\n如果有下次，差唔多價錢我會買出前一丁好過。"},{"pid":"ee5d1a8db0af0566e65ba1c66e9150111f64e8b1","tid":1011140,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"第一次睇到嗰陣以為真係有蟹味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470ccb16423462c2d0bbf6079c85370565688a9e","tid":1011140,"uid":204728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14b97719d5b74d5af30533ac6f815af138f206c","tid":1011140,"uid":5846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ee5d1a8db0af0566e65ba1c66e9150111f64e8b1","tid":1011140,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"第一次睇到嗰陣以為真係有蟹味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"我諗係蟹貨個蟹"},{"pid":"3c9ff7cfeefb3e5d0b99c6b772d5d762724c9253","tid":1011140,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"其實好普通"},{"pid":"49b0583081f752b6a68309dc10459fe8a2d071d9","tid":1011140,"uid":37966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"Ching 隻煎蛋 🍳好正bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c06dc2712dc7ebecaf269c040141c5d2c7cdc","tid":1011140,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"易入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有咩即食麵湯係難入口？"},{"pid":"42d4800ab69622538dbbd66808c336235e8d439a","tid":1011140,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"根本吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94aaabfbf772d206a850e9de7c1f3e49cf51cd2f","tid":1011140,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"食過一次唔好食 食出前一丁仲好"}]}